---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Games Art International Assembly 2025" description="Games Art International Assembly 2025" />
		<style>

			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				display: flex;
				font-size: 14px;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				min-height: 100vh;

			}
			.content {
				flex-grow: 1;
				padding: 60px;
				max-width: 800px;
				width: 100%;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			.game-section {
				margin-bottom: 60px;
			}
			.game-title {
				font-size: 24px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;


			}
			
			.image-gallery {
				display: flex;
				overflow-x: auto;
				gap: 20px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
				-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
			}
			.gallery-item {
				flex: 0 0 auto;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 533px;
				height: 300px;
			}
			.gallery-video {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
			.gallery-image {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: cover;
			}
			.game-description {
				max-width: 600px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;
				white-space: pre-wrap;

			}
			.game-credits {
				margin-top: 12px;
				max-width: 600px;
			}
			.game-credits ul {
				margin: 4px 0 0 0;
				padding-left: 20px;
			}
			.video-embed {
				position: relative;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 600px;
				padding-top: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
				margin: 20px 0;
			}
			.video-embed iframe {
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				border: 0;
			}
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				body {
					flex-direction: column;
				}
				.content {
					padding: 20px;
				}
				.game-title {
					font-size: 20px;
				}
				.gallery-item {
					height: 56.25vw; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
					max-height: 300px;
				}
				.game-description {
					font-size: 14px;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Sidebar />
		<div class="content">
			<strong>Games Art International Assembly 2025</strong>
			<br>
			Barcelona, Spain
			<br>
			2025
            <br>
            <hr>
            <br>
            Talk: Thoughtful Human Curation Against Algoirthmic Fuelled Monopolistic Platforms
			<p>
            The Game Arts International Assembly (GAIA) is an international think tank and network for the professional development of the game arts community: aimed at curators, producers, event organizers and academics working in the field of videogame culture. </p>

            <p>
            GAIA addresses topics such as: curation, art and videogames, activism, communication, language, communities, minorities, funding, networks, archiving and many more.
			<p>
            
            <p>GAIA 2025 took place in Barcelona, Spain. It included 30 speakers from 19 countries and 14 sessions over 3 days + field trips. I gave an in-person talk about thoughtful games curation, introducing the early developments of my curation platform <a href="https://www.exhibitplay.com">Exhibit:Play</a>.
            </p>

            <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1TNAsfidOE478nzihyIGkjR-SSUUVLtKc/view"><img src="/gaia-2025/gaia-report-title.webp"/></a>
            <caption>Click the image to view the full 35 page GAIA 2025 report</caption>
            <br>
            <br>
            <img src="/gaia-2025/gaia-browser-shows.webp"/>
            <caption>A page from the report summarizing three talks under the theme of "Browser Shows"</caption>
            <br>
            <br>
            <img src="/gaia-2025/gaia-1.webp"/>
            <caption>Group discussion and tour of Fundació Foto Colectania with curator Jon Uriarte</caption>
            <br>
            <br>
            <img src="/gaia-2025/gaia-2.webp"/>
            <caption>Me giving my talk</caption>
            <br>
            <br>
            <img src="/gaia-2025/gaia-3.webp"/>
            <caption>One of the group workshops</caption>
            <br>
            <br>
            <img src="/gaia-2025/gaia-4.webp"/>
            <caption>Group photo of all GAIA 2025 participants</caption>



		</div>
	</body>
</html>